{"word":"G3166 - μεγαλαυχέω - megalauchéō - meg-al-ow-kheh'-o - Boast great things","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεγαλαυχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>megalauchéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>meg-al-ow-kheh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Boast great things"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெருமையானவைகளைப் பேசு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be grandiloquent; to boast great things, to bear oneself loftily in speech or action"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3173 - μέγας - mégas - meg'-as/3173\">G3173</a> and <b>&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>aucheo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>boast</i>; akin to <a href=\"#/G837 - αὐξάνω - auxánō - owx-an'-o/837\">G837</a> and <a href=\"#/G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee/2744\">G2744</a>); to <i>talk big</i>, that is, <i>be grandiloquent</i> (<i>arrogant</i>, <i>egotistic</i>): - boast great things."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}